---
import BrandLayout from "../layouts/BrandLayout.astro";
---

<BrandLayout
  slug=""
  eyebrow="AVA Golf"
  title="Brand Guidelines"
  subtitle="Guidelines on how to implement and use the AVA Golf brand."
  variant="hero"
>
  <div slot="hero-cta" class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
    <a
      href="/files/AVA_Golf_Brand_Pack.zip"
      download
      class="text-button hover:bg-yellow-300 hover:text-dark-green-900 inline-flex h-12 w-80 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-yellow-300 text-white transition-colors"
      style="letter-spacing:0.1em;"
    >
      Download Brand Pack
    </a>
    <p class="text-micro text-bright-green-500">V1.0.0</p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[750px]">
    <p class="text-label text-green-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">
      Introduction
    </p>
    <div class="text-body text-dark-green-700 space-y-5">
      <p>
        Our brand is built on consistency — not as a constraint, but as a mark of confidence.
These guidelines establish how the AVA Golf brand is expressed across every context:
the visual language, tone of voice, and communication principles that make every
interaction recognizable, intentional, and true to who we are.
      </p>
      <p>
        Within these pages you'll find everything needed to represent AVA Golf with precision, 
from visual elements and logo usage through to voice, values, and audience. Used
well, these guidelines ensure every touchpoint reflects a brand built for serious golfers
and the people who share their ambition.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BrandLayout>
